description: This hall of fame Gatinho purrs with a rating of 54, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 270, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 5 for East, Box for South, and Stringalong for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [270 Votes, Hall of Fame]
